'''Leonardo di ser Piero da Vinci''' ( 14/15 abril 1452 - 2 mayyu 1519), 
ittyawssan s '''Leonardo da Vinci''', ikka-t-nn iga yan ugtusnak [[Talyan|aṭalyani]] iddren ɣ tleslalit, iruran taynit dar kigan n yigran zun d [[unuɣ]], [[taklut]], "sculpture", [[tasedga]], [[tussna]], [[Azawan|aẓawan]], [[tusnakt]], tajenyurit, [[tasekla]], "anatomie", [[tusnakalt]], [[tasnallunt]], tasnemɣit, "paléontologie", d "cartographie". 
Ikka-t-nn Leonardo ar ittiri ad yisin akkʷ mad illan f [[ugama]], ad yisin manka s teswuri ku taɣawsa, ikka-t-nn iḥrec bahra ɣ tiɣri, "designing" d usgadda n kraygatt asekkin. 

Ar ttannayen kigan n mdden Leonardo mas iga yan zeɣ yimeklawen akkʷ mqqurnin ɣ umezruy, wiyyaḍ ar t-ttannayen zund umayaf-nnsen akkʷ. Tenna fell-as tanmezruyt n tẓuri Helen Gardner mas d ur jju izri mad t-irwasen, acku ikka-t-inn ar iggar taynit-nnes s ugudi n tɣawsiwin zund is ur ili anelli-nnes iwetta. Ar tizi-ad nit ur ta jju nessen yat f manka s tt-inn tekka "caractère"-nnes.  

Ilul-d ɣ ammas n [[Vinci]], yat tiɣremt imeẓẓin illan tama n [[Flurinsa]] ɣ [[Talyan|Ṭṭalyan]]. Ittuselɣem f ufus n "sculptor" d umekla [[Andrea del Verrocchio]] afad ad imɣur ayg anaẓur, izzri tudert-nnes s umata-nnes, ar gi-s iswuri dar kra n yiristuqraṭiyen iṭalyanen bahra bɣernin. Ɣ yiseggʷasen-nnes ggʷuranin, idder ɣ yat tgemmi ifulkin nna as-ifka ugellid n [[Fransa|Fṛansa]]. 

Ar tettyawḥasabent snat ɣ tugniwin-nnes f tugniwin akkʷ dar mi illa waddur ɣ umaḍal, ad tent-igan d Mona Lisa d The last supper (Imensi ameggaru), isker ula agudi n wunuɣen, yan bahra gi-sen ittyawssanen zund Vitruvian Man (Argaz Awvitruv). Ɣ umata n tikkal, ikka-t-inn Leonardo ar bedda iswingim ɣ yisnulfuten imaynutnin, ilin bedda di-s kra n walugen ɣ ittzemmam akkʷ unuɣen d tektiyin-nnes, amata ɣ yisnulfuten-nnes ur ten jju sul ismed. Rad gi-sen naf kra n tektiyin zun d "hélicoptère", "tank", tamsiḍent, "parachute", aṛubu, atilifun, tiẓri n tneflit d "énergie solaire".
