==Tudert-nnes==
===Timẓi-nnes, 1452-1466===
[[Afaylu:Study of a Tuscan Landscape.jpg|thumb|Unuɣ akkʷ iqburen dar Leonardo f uyenna ittwassnen, Asif n Arnu, 1473. Illa ɣ usefser n Uffizi.|259x259px]]

Ilul Leonardo ɣ 15 abril 1452, ɣ tiɣremt tatuskanit n [[Vinci]], ɣ yiɣzer n wasif Arnu, yura jeddis [[Antonio da Vinci]] ifruriten n tlalit-nnes acku ur ta tahlen imarawen-nnes ɣakud-ann, iga iwwi-s n [[Ser Piero da Vinci]], yan umsentam awflurintin bahra ibeɣren, d Caterina, yat tmazzalt nna f ggudin iwenniten d teẓriyin, illa mad fell-as ittinin mas tt-nn tekka tga yat tesmegt d-ikkan beṛṛa n tmazirt-nnsen, zun d [[Ccinwa]] neɣ d Anẓul-Agmuḍan, yili daɣ mayd ittinin mas tt-nn tekka ur tgi abla yat tmeẓluḍt ult tmazirt-nnsen nit. D Leonardo, Iɣʷi-t-nn sul dars babas ikellef sis, tiwel daɣ yemmas turu semmus wazzanen yaḍnin. Isem nnes ummid igat "Leonardo di ser Piero da Vinci", isnumken "Leonardo, iwwis n mass Pier u Vinci".

Izzri Leonardo semmus ɣ yiseggʷasen-nnes imezwura d yemmas ɣ yat tgemmi mm wurti, fad ilemma immuti s Vinci ad izdeɣ d ibbas d temɣart-nnes tis-snat Albiera, ilin di-sen ula id jeddis d ɛemmis Francesco. Ḍart mad imeqqur Leonardo, ur bahra izemmim f temẓi-nnes abla yan sin yikettayen ẓlinin, amezwaru lliɣ t-nn-ikka iẓẓel yan wass beṛṛa ujguggel-nnes, yuyel nnig-as yan ugḍiḍ ixatren isli-t s rric-nnes ɣ udem-nnes. Akettay-nnes azalan wis-sin igat; lliɣ t-nn-ikka ar issara yan udrar yaf-nn yan ifri, d mqqar t-nn ikka iksuḍ ad yili kra n xxu ɣ ugens, ur t-tujji tdewwayt-nnes ad ser-s ikcim ad gi-s isnubbec.

===Tasawert n Verrocchio, 1466-1476===

Ɣ 1466, lliɣ t-nn-tekka dar Leonardo 14 useggʷas, yiwi-t-nn babas dar Flurinsa, afad ad ig anelmad n unaẓur [[Andrea del Verrocchio|Verrocchio]]. 

Tekka-tt-nn tga Flurinsa yan udɣar ismectagen ul n yan umeẓyan innurzen ad yaɣul d anaẓur, ddren gi-s yad kigan n inaẓuren ttyawssanin ɣ temrawant n 1200 zun d Cimabue d Giotto, ɣinna dar ibeṛṛem yan ixef-nnes qad nn gi-s yaf ifarsen iẓuranen ẓilnin ttyawssanin, ha takatidralit takeswatt s talqubbet-nnes tamaynut igan tabarawt, ha taglizt n ugʷrram John s tiggura-nnes n wureɣ sfiqqisnint, tili ɣ tama-nnes yat teglizt-yaḍen mi ssutulen wattayen-nnes "sculptures" d-kkanin "sculpteurs" akkʷ ttyawssannin zun d aselmad n Leonardo s yixef-nnes. 

Anaẓur igan aleḥyan ɣakud-ann iga-t wa d yufan kra n umassaɣ i tfelwin-nnes, yan lli rad tent dar-s yawi s tugt-nnsent. Tawja akkʷ ibeɣren ɣ Flurinsa n uzemz-ann [[Medici]] ad tt-igan, nettni ad dar ikka ubergemmi akkʷ ifejjijen ammas n temdint-ann, d iɛezza dar-sen ad ssaɣen tifelwin, isefrisen d tɣawsiwin yaḍnin ẓilnin, kkan-t-nn awed ar bahra ttraran taynit s tsekla d tfelsuft, kigan d inaẓuren iɛerrimen ɣakud-ann; kkan ar ttnuruzen ad si-sen raren ayt Medici d yimeddukkal-nnsen taynit. 

Tezri dar Verrocchio yat tsawert imeqquren ur isalan, ɣ ikka Leonardo ar ittelmad tiɣarasin n [[Taẓuri|tẓuri]], ɣik-ann ma f t-nn fell-as ikka iga ccil ad ilmed unuɣ, taklut, "sculpture" d umsudem. Mac ɣ wakud igan yan, ilmed daɣ kraygatt tasugert tunfiɛt illan, zun d takrura, tagemɣuzt, tagebbaṣt, tawuri n yilmawen, tamikanikt d tnesramt. 

Ur d Leonardo i waḍu-nnes ka ɣinn ikkan ɣ tsawert-ann, amunen gi-s agudi n yimeklawen-yaḍnin, yili akkʷ gi-sen mad yaɣulen d "célèbre" imeqquren, zun d [[Domenico Ghirlandaio|Ghirlandaio]], Perugino d [[Sandro Botticelli|Botticelli]]. Inaẓuren-ad, ur bahra ugren Leonardo s yiseggʷasen. Ar ittales Giorgio Vasari yat tenfust ilan azal f tizi-ad ɣ tudert n Leonardo, ɣ t-nn-ikka Verrocchio ar ikellu yat tfelwit ixatren iqqnen s wudum (baptême) n umasiḥ, ifka-as i Leonardo tmehla n ad iklu yan ɣ yineglusen illan f uẓelmaḍ-nnes. Inna Vasari mas t-nn ikʷla Leonardo s yat tmamekt imk-ad ifulkin, isres-nn akkʷ Verrocchio ccita-nnes s yat tikkelt, d ur jju d nettan ad sul iklu kra ɣ tudert-nnes. S yan uzzray ineɣden, rad ifrek yan i mas d Leonardo ad ixedmen ula igezzumen-ann-nnes yaḍnin, zun d izṛan, amzaz aqehwi d ula "background-nnes". Ar ttinin ula f Leonardo mas d fell-as isnulfa Verrocchio ɣakud-ann asefris-nnes awbrunẓ n David isker gi-s zund tmudemt-nnes. [[Afaylu:Leonardo Magi.jpg|thumb|250px|''Baḍaḍ n umajus'', (1481) ɣ usefser n Uffizi]]Ɣ 1472 zun d ɣik-ann, lliɣ t-nn dar-s tekka 20 useggʷas, ilkem-d Leonardo "Guild" n St Luke (Luke Agʷrram), yat tmaddast n yinaẓuren d yiḍukturen n tesnijjit, d mqqar as-d-isersel ibba-s yat tsawert igan tinnes i yixef-nnes, iɣama-nn Leonardo dar Verrocchio izdeɣ dars acku tɛezza dars twwuri ɣinna. 

Tawuri akkʷ iqburen dar Leonardo f uyenna ittyawssanen iga-t unuɣ n wasif Arnu ittyawskaren s uɣanib, ittuzemmem s usakud n 5 ɣuct 1473, yili ɣila ɣ usefser n Uffinzi.

===Tudert-nnes tazzulant, 1476-1499===
Adday ittara Vasari f Leonardo, ar issemras kra n yiwaliwen zun d "noble", amafkay, "gracieux" d ufalkay, ar aɣ ittini Vasari mas t-nn-ikka Leonardo ɣ tiɛɛurma-nnes, iga yan urgaz iɣezzifen ifulkin, ikka-t-nn idus kigan igeḍḍer, ar akkʷ issefraɣ tisaliwin n yisan s yifassen-nnes qqurnin. Iẓil bahra umesli-nnes ar si-s "charmer" wanna as ka isellan, isiggel kraygatt yan tiddukkla-nnes ɣakud-ann. Ikka-t-nn iga yan umeccimɣan dar ɛezzan imudar, ar issaɣ kra tikkal igḍaḍ afad ad ten ka isderfi. 

Ikka-t-nn Leonardo iga yan unaẓur ilan yat tmefkit imqqurn, isnulfa-d ɣ 1482 yat "lyre" n uẓref (nnqert) f talɣa n yixef n wayyis, tizi ɣ t-nn-ikka yan unebbaḍ amaynu ɣ temdint n Milan agafa n Ṭṭalyan, igan s yisem Ludovico il Moro, yan uduk isennuɣjufen inebbaḍen yaḍnin. Yuzen Lorenzo n ayt Medici Leonardo s Milan zund umesqad-nnes afad ad ifek i Ludovico Lyre-ann-nnes zund yat trezzift zeɣ dars. Yura Leonardo i uduk n Milan yat tebratt, ɣ ittales kullu tiɣawsiwin-ann ḥrecnin unfiɛnin nna mi izḍar, zun d asnulfu n tmacinin n girra. Yara-as ula s uzegzel mas "issen i teklut ula nettat", ur t-nn akkʷ ikki ɣ ugayyu-nnes ɣakud-ann mas d taɣawsa-ad nit s rad bahra sul ittyawssan. Iɣama-nn Leonardo ɣ Milan ar iswuri dar uduk ger iseggʷasen n 1482 d 1499, ikka dars yan ugezzum ɣ twwuri-nnes iẓlin ɣar s "design" n "défilés" n tfugliwin d ikaṛnabalen, ttyafan dars ula ɣ walugen-nnes kra n wunuɣen i tmelsa n tmezgunin, idsen yimsegdalen "incroyable" d kra n yisinaryuten nna mi yallfus ad ilin assaɣ d umezgun. [[Afaylu:Study of horse.jpg|thumb|Tazrawt n Leonardo da Vinci s tneqqiḍt n uẓref i ''Ayyis'', c. 1488]]Leonardo, zun d nettan zun d amata n yinaẓuren bahra ttyawssannin ɣ uzemz-nnes, kkan-t-nn dar-s idsen yimazzalen ɣ tsawert-nnes, swa inelmaden iɛerrimen swa imawasen meqqurnin, ikka-t-nn yan ɣ yinelmaden-nnes iga s yisem Gian Giacomo Caprotti da Oren. Ikka-t-nn iga yan urba iɣudan iṭṭafen "curls" n wureɣ ɣezzifnin fulkinin. Ikka-t-inn ar di-s ittacka ad ig tamudemt n yineglusen dar yinaẓuren. Mac iga ula yan uxendallas iceqqan, "Salai" neɣ "Salaino" (isnumken "iblis imeẓẓin") ka ad as-ittini Leonardo. 

Yura Leonardo ɣ walug-nnes f Salai, mas t-nn-ikka iga yan uṭemmaɛ d yan bu tkerkas ur ilin anaw, d mas t-nn-ikka ar as bedda ittaker tiɣawsiwin-nnes ɣ tgemmi, idder di-s ɣ ammas n uzedduɣ-nnes i 30 yiseggʷasen zund unelmad d umazzal-nnes.

====''Ayyis Axatar''====
Afares n Leonardo akkʷ ilan azal ɣakud-ann ɣ uzemz n uswuri dar Ludovico, iga-t asnulfu n yan usefris imqquren f talɣa n yan umnay issudan ayyis-nnes, ad si-s ssimɣuren s unebbaḍ-nnsen izwaren Francesco Sforza. Izwur-d Leonardo s wayyis, deffir mad bahra isker tezrawin-nnss f "anatomie" n wanaw-a ɣ yimudar, issuneɣ-asen id "design"; isnulfa-d yan wayyis n tallaɣt imqquren mi iga s yisem "Gran Cavallo" (Ayyis Axatar), ikka-t-nn rad as sul ittuga ubrunẓ-nnes afad ad yaɣul ayyis awbrunẓ akkʷ ixatren ɣ umezruy atrar. Mac ur as sul tettusmid twwuri-nnes s temgeṛẓa. Ɣ 1494, ifka Ludovico abrunẓ-ann akkʷ dar-sen illan ad t-nn-ssurrin s "cannons" acku fell-asen d-ikcem userdas afṛansis s uwettas n usdurriy. [[Ayyis]] n tallaɣt ixatren, ibidd ukan tizi-ann ɣ rad d-urrin ifransisen s Milan ɣ 1499 afad ad daɣ armen ad tt-sdurriyen, smersen-t tikkelt-ad i usleɣmu n tniyyact, xlun-t kullu.

====''Tamgudt n Isulilen''====
[[Afaylu:Study for the Sforza Monument.jpg|thumb|Tazrawt s tneqqiḍt n uẓref i umedruz (design ittwajjen), c.&nbsp;1490]]Izzri Leonardo snat tseqqimin n teklut nna mi dar illa wazal ɣ wakud ɣ t-nn-ikka ar iswuri dar Ludovico. Yat gi-sent; ad iklu yat tfelwit n uzatim (zzit) nna rad iddun s useɣres axatar n tegʷmat n usemmeḍren iɣusen (Confraternity of the immaculate conception), isker gi-s Leonardo snat tfelwin ifel-d yat d yimhiwac n Milan, yiwi di-s ṭayya s Franṣa, tɣama-nn. Ad tettyafa ɣassa ɣ usalay n Louvre. 

Ur mzarayent tfelwin ad s yisem, ar mmalant s sin-itsent amuɣli n Maryam Tamgudt d bijju-nnes [[Ɛisa]], ɣ ammas n yan udɣar ameḍlus igan kullu isulilen,َ mani ɣ rad mmaggaren d John Amseddam. Tella yat tenfust (nna ur illin ɣ [[Injil]], tili ɣar ɣ taysi tawmasiḥt) f manik as imlala [[Ɛisa]] bijju d John ɣ uɣaras ittawin s [[Miṣra|Misṛa]]. Ɣ tmuɣli-a, illa John ar ittẓalla; yall-d [[Ɛisa]] bijju afus-nnes ibarek-t. Tettyawssan tfelwit-ad n Leonardo s unezwi-ann-nnes ikerrmen nna aɣ-takka, asidd-nnes aɣrib ikkaten s yan usyafa ittawin tiysas, imula-nnes dranin d "background"-nnes immalan agelmam d yidurar ɣ ammas n taggut. Ur jjun akkʷ tettyawskar kra n tfelwit igan zun d nettat ɣ kullu mayd izrin.[[Afaylu:Leonardo Da Vinci - Vergine delle Rocce (Louvre).jpg|thumb|left|''Tamgudt n Isulilen'', Louvre, yallfus is d 1505–1508.]]

====''Imensi Ameggaru''====
Tafelwit tis-snat n Leonardo ɣ [[Milan]] nna mi dar illa wazal, is akkʷ tettyawssan uggar n tiyyaḍ. Nettat ad igan s yisem Imensi Ameggaru (the Last Supper), ar temmala imensi akkʷ igguran dar [[Ɛisa]] s tamunt n yimeḥḍaren-nnes dat wammaẓ d menɣiwt-nnes. Ista Leonardo ad iklu imir-ann ɣ ittini Ɛisa "rad iyi gi-wen iɣḍer kra n yan", ar ittales Leonardo addad n ubhaḍ d unnuɣjef nna d-iɣʷin yineḍfaren-nnes s simraw, ar t-ittales s uɣaras n yimuggan d wudmawen n mdden ɣ ammas n tfelwit. Idsen ar sawalen, idsen bidden, idsen ar ttalen ɣ yifassen-nnsen s tiwdi. 

Ikka-t-nn uneggal Matteo Bandello ar iẓerra Leonardo ɣ ammas n twuri-nnes. Yura fell-as mas d ar izzray mennaw n wussan; ar ka ikellu akkʷ mad ila wass s bla n tiremt, ibidd daɣ ilemma kṛaḍ neɣ d kkuẓ n wussan-yaḍnin bla gi-sen iklu wala isker yat, kra n tikkal; ar ka ɣinn ittṣemmar mnid n tfelwin-nnes ar gi-sen ittqezzaz. Inna Vasari mas as-ɣʷlin idammen i umɣar n teɣzamt tamhawcant, itter-as ad isneɣmes Leonardo s mas as-d-iqqan ad iswurri s timmri. Inna Vasari mas t-nn-ikka Leonardo ittecṭen akkʷ, acku ur inni d yixef-nnes is rad nit iẓḍar ad isgadda udem n Ɛisa mezyan, inna-as i uduk mas yallfus is rad isker ɣ wudem n umɣar n yimhiwac tamudemt-nnes i Judas ameɣdar.[[Afaylu:Última Cena - Da Vinci 5.jpg|thumb|400px|"Imensi Ameggaru" (1498). Milan, Italy.]]

Deffir mad tesmed twuri n tfelwit, nnan fell-as kullu willi tt-ẓranin s umata-nnsen mas d tawuri-nnes tamayuft akkʷ ayenna. 

Maca ur as yad issemres Leonardo i tfelwit-ann "fresco" as-d-yusan, isker-as "tempera" iggi n gissu (gesso), nna ur aɣ ittusemrasen yad-lli i tfelwin n uɣrab. ɣik-ann ma f as-ittca tɣurdin-nnes txemmej kullu, terwi s yat tikkelt ḍart yat tmiḍi yiseggʷasen. Mqqar d-iḍer uklu n kra ɣ idɣaren-nnes zeɣ uɣrab, tekka-t-inn tfelwit-ann tettyawssan kigan, ancet-ann lli gi-s ittusiggzen-ittusneɣlen yuger kullu tifelwin tisegdanin n umaḍal.

===Tudert-nnes tazzulant, 1499-1513===

Ɣ 1499, seḍren Ludovico il Moro. Immuti Leonardo zeɣ Milan d umazzal-nnes Salai d umeddakkl-nnes amusnak Luca Pacioli s Vinisya. Iswuri ɣinna Leonardo zund kran umasgad d ujenyur aserdasan. Acku tga Vinisya yat temdint ibidden f kigan n tegzirin, yurem Leonardo ad iswingim ɣ itsent tɣarasin ma s fell-as ittegdal azzaɣen n iɣerruba. Ɣ 1500, yurri-d Leonardo s Flurinsa s tamunt n yimazzalen d yinelmaden-nnes. Fkan-as imhiwac n teɣzamt "Holy Annunciation" yat taddart d yat tsawert imeqquren.

