====''Tamgudt d urba d Anne Tagʷrramt d John Amseddam''====

Ibda Leonardo tawuri f yat tfelwit yaḍen, ig-nn yan uɣawas ɣ yixef-nnes issuneɣ-as yat tunuɣt imeqquren; immalan Mayram Tamgudt, tsekkus f ufud n yemmas Anne Tagʷrramt tusi di-s abijju-nnes Ɛisa, yili f ufasi-nnes John Amseddam (Baptist). Inna Vasari mas tsebheḍ tunuɣt-ann tafalkayt akkʷ midden, ddan-d ad tt-annin irgazen d tmeṭṭutin, imeẓyiyn wala wid meqqurnin s tigrummawin, ad tinid is d kra n umuggar imqquren a s d-uckan. Ar tettyafa ɣila tunuɣt-ad ɣ Usefser Anamur, London. Mqqar d bahra teqbur tezzef, tili ammas n yat tmeṣriyt illasen, da ttekkan midden kraygatt ass asefser-nnes afad ad ka skubbren mind-nnes. Zun d nettat zun d mennawt g twuriwin n Leonardo, ur as jju ismed tafelwit-nnes.

====''Imenɣi n Anghiari''====
[[Afaylu:After leonardo da vinci, The Battle of Anghiari by Rubens, Louvre.jpg|thumb|250px|tad tga tunɣilt i tfelwit n Leonardo igan s yisem" Imenɣi n Anghiari" nna tt-nn-ikkan ittuxlan, iga-as aɣrab addal ɣ wattayen n 1560; yallfus is tga tunɣilt-ad aɣawas i tfelwit]]
Ɣ 1502 d 1503, iswuri Leonardo dar Cesare Borgia, aristuqraṭ idusen iwwi-s n ubaba Alexander wis-sḍis. Ikka-t-nn Leonardo ar di-s ittmuddu zund kran umasgad d ujenyur aserdasan, ar ttekkan mennaw idɣaren ugens n Ṭṭalyan. Tigiriwin n 1503, yurri-d Leonardo s Flurinsa, ilkem-d "Guild" n Luke Agʷrram i tikkelt-yaḍen. 

Tettufka-as yat tmeskirt bahra istawhemman zeɣ dar useqqim (Signoria) n Flurinsa, ran-t ad asen-iklu yan zeɣ sin "frescos"-ann mqqurnin nna rad ilin ɣ ammas n yiɣerban n tmeṣriyt akkʷ dar mi illa wazal ɣ ubergemmi n useqqim-nna, ittukellaf Michelangelo s teklut n Imenɣi n Cascina, ikellef Leonardo s tin Imenɣi n Anghiari. Issenta Leonard ɣ usenfar-nnes, isker tezrawin-nnes f udmawen n yirgazen rfanin d yiysan-nnsen mmaɣnin, issuneɣ-ten, ilin ukan sul unuɣen-a ar ɣilad ɣ walugen-nnes. Mac s temgeṛẓa, rad daɣ ig uya yan "failure" zeɣ dar Leonardo, acku lliɣ nn-ikʷla tugna-ann ɣ uɣrab, ɣ udɣar n ad issemres "fresco", ismerkes-as ikʷlan-nnes d uzatim (zzit), ɣik-ann ma-f as-ggammin ad zwun. Lliɣ yurem ad ten-issreɣ s imikk n wafa, tefsi-as tfelwit kullu-tt. Issuneɣ Peter Paul yat tunɣilt i ugezzum-nnes anammas, awin-as-d ayt useqqim n teɣremt ḍart yat tizi ma rad as daɣ yalsen ɣ uɣrab. Ur ikemmel Michelangelo tafelwit-nnes ula netta acku as-iɣra ubaba s Ruma.

====''Mona Lisa''====
[[Afaylu:Mona Lisa, by Leonardo da Vinci, from C2RMF retouched.jpg|thumb|''[[Mona Lisa]]'' neɣ d ''La Gioconda'' (1503–1519)—[[Louvre]], Bariz, Fṛansa]]

Ɣ wattayen n 1503, ibda Leonardo ar ikellu tafelwit n yat tmɣart ittyawssanen s Mona Lisa, tasefrist akkʷ nna mi dar illa waddur nger kullu tifelwin yaḍnin. Mennaw yiseggʷasen ad gi-s izzri, tga yat tugna imeẓẓin ittwaklun s uzatim (zzit) iggi n yan yifil n ukccuḍ. Ar temmala udem, tafegga tanafellant d yifassen n yat tmɣart ilsan zund ku ass. Ɣ tsefrisin, ar yad-lli tlessa tamɣart timelsa d tzuzaf-nnes timayufnin. Tles ɣid Mona Lisa yat tqendurt iḍlan d yan waddal aseggan afella yixef-nnes. Ɣ umata n tikkal, ar ittajja Leonardo ɣ tfelwin-nnes kra n yizumal ma's yakka kra n tmula (indices) f umdan nna gi-sen ittilin. Ayenn igan aɣrib ɣ tugna ya d uyenna igan aɣbalu i yisem nna s tettyawssan iga-t uzmummeg-nnes : Mona Lisa Giaconda, ar tesnamek Giaconda "tanna itteṣṣan", (tga Mona azegzel n Madonna isnumken "Lalla-nu".)

Tamentilt n max aylliɣ bahra tettyawssan tfelwit-ad, iga-t acku tektur s yidrigen, ar nn-ttaggʷan allen n Mona Lisa s yinigi-nnes, mac ur inni ta yan ad d-ildi ayenn issaran ixef-nnes. Allen-nnes d ula imi-nnes, ar ttumanen zund is aɣ zmummugen, tamsalt igan tamaynut ɣ teklut n tsefrisin, acku ar gi-s yad-lli ttumanen midden s umata-nnsen gan "sérieux". Iceqqa ad yakez yan tinfaliyin n wudem n Mona Lisa s usenɣed, acku iɣ yad ira yan ad iɣer isyafaten n wayya yakez-ten, iqqan-t-id ad nn-iluḥ asmaqqel-nnes s usga n tɣemriwin n wallen d yimawen-nnsen. Ixdem-tt Leonardo s yat tɣarast ɣ tettumanen imula fessusnin ɣ tseggiwin n udem, ameggerḍ d yifassen-nnes, ar tettusemma tamamekt-a "sfumato" (isnumken "aggu" s taṭalyanit). Ḍart mad tt-ẓran kra n yinaẓuren-yaḍnin, nnan d yiguyya-nnsen mas d ur rad zḍaren i teklut n kra n tfelwit igan zun d nettat.

===Tudert-nnes tazzulant, 1506-1516===

Ɣ 1506, yurri-d Leonardo s Milan d yinelmaden-nnes, idder ɣ tgemmi-nnes ɣ ammas n Porta Orientale. Aɣulen idsen ɣ yinelmaden-nnes d imeklawen : Bernardino Luini, Giovanni Antonio Boltraffio d Marco D'Oggione. Isker D'Oggione mennawt tunɣilin i Imensi Ameggaru, isker Luini yat i Tamgudt n Isulilen, ikʷla Boltraffio d wiyyaḍ kigan n tugniwin n id Madonna d Ubijju, izḍar yan ad tent sul iẓer ɣ yisefsar n tẓuri d ula tiglizin.

